<p><span>10</span><span>月</span><span>20</span><span>日，联想通过线上直播的</span><span>方式举办</span><span>了</span><span>一场</span><span>秋季新品发布会。此次发布会</span><span>的精彩程度不容分说，正如</span><span>发布会</span><span>主题“精彩不止一屏”</span><span>所</span><span>描述的一样，联想</span><span>这次带来了</span><span>不止</span><span>联想小新</span><span>Pro</span><span></span><span>14</span><span></span><span>2021</span><span>这一款重磅级产品</span><span>，</span><span>还包括</span><span>联想</span><span>小新</span><span>Air 14 2021</span><span>、联想小新</span><span>Air15 2021</span><span>以及</span><span>小新</span><span>Pad</span><span>平板</span><span>等</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>而</span><span>联想旗下</span><span>YOGA</span><span>品牌</span><span>则</span><span>发布了</span><span>YOGA 14s 2021</span><span>、</span><span>YOGA 14c 2021</span><span>、</span><span>YOGA 13s 2021</span><span>、</span><span>YOGA Pro 13s Carbon 2021</span><span>四款笔记本新品和</span><span>YOGA 27</span><span>多功能一体电脑</span><span>。</span><span>全系</span><span>新品</span><span>以“好屏幕”为主打亮点，</span><span>并且还有高性能释放和好散热以及好音响等值得加分的属性。</span></p>
<p><span>下面我们就来回顾一下</span><span>这些</span><span>产品亮点。</span></p>
<p><span><strong>YOGA</strong></span><span><strong></strong></span><span><strong>27</strong></span><span><strong>一体机</strong></span></p>
<p><span>YOGA</span><span></span><span>27</span><span>一体机是一款非常灵活</span><span>，告别单一维度</span><span>的</span><span>多功能</span><span>一体电脑产品，</span><span>用户可通过一键切换改变它的形态，包括“一体电脑”模式、笔记本</span><span>/</span><span>手机的“一线连”模式、大屏影音无线投屏的“无线投”模式</span><span>，不仅可以为笔记本提供</span><span>65W</span><span>的供电，而且还能将一体机标配的</span><span>2T</span><span>硬盘容量分享给笔记本，实现数据共享和备份。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201022/02d7b6104a2c49e4a7efefbda55174d0.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>作为一款大屏设备，</span><span>YOGA27</span><span>的</span><span>屏幕</span><span>也很出色</span><span>，</span><span>采用了</span><span>27</span><span>英寸</span><span>4K</span><span>分辨率显示器，具备</span><span>99% Adobe RGB/DCI-P3</span><span>色域</span><span>，可以满足专业用户</span><span>制图</span><span>需求</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201022/4e775f1335ab4c6fbd45b7f42ec9c679.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
